==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reticulation
<hw>Re*tic`u*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
or state of being reticulated, or netlike; that which is reticulated;
network; an organization resembling a net.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The particular net you occupy in the great
<qex>reticulation</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Carlyle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reticule</ent>⟦br⟧
